title: Shovel Knight's retail release delayed two weeks
text:
Shovel Knight's retail release delayed two weeks 
Published By: Eurogamer.net - Today 
Shovel Knight's retail release was originally scheduled for next week, but it's just been delayed a fortnight. Now it's set for 30th October...
